name: The Boneyard
description:
The resting place of gods, the celestial boneyard was called Elysium.
Now, the Elysian Fields were mythical.

There was no possible way to prove that they existed.
After all, some people couldn't even see the sun.

Gazing upon their marble peaks, the mortals saw a comfortable space.
They were not too hot or too cold.

It was good there.
